{"tid":916872,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我好迷茫，有無人可以幫下手？","createTime":"2018-11-26T03:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T09:58:38.000Z","uid":167086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5253334a029dc96a2e8396929ae30b1985c6dc1c","tid":916872,"uid":167086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"話說我之前中意左個女仔一年，明戀左佢好耐，而佢都好似幾受<br />\n但過多一排，我識左第二個女仔，大家識得唔耐就一齊咗(ps.佢追我)<br />\n依家都一齊咗年幾，但我依家先發覺其實仲鍾意我之前暗戀果個，我又唔想咁唔負責任就咁離開依家呢個，大家點睇？"},{"pid":"7692c5c75a55e6e43581be0b254baac5c865b4a0","tid":916872,"uid":167086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9effb0ca87041acadcc1984e2a2e88e24c6a515c","tid":916872,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:58:38.000Z","msg":"呀姐笑多幾日 笑多幾日就唔肚痛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}